      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-ctr-ele        >    w-rig-num-ele
                     go to stp-cor-doc-870.
           if        w-rig-ctr-ele        >    w-rig-max-ele
                     go to stp-cor-doc-870.
