      *                      * Bufferizzazione progressivo riga        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bfr-num-prg       to   w-rig-key-prg-13
                                              (w-rig-num-ele)         .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad uscita                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-o01-900.
       stp-cor-doc-o01-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-o01-999.
       stp-cor-doc-o01-999.
