      *                  * Se errore di start : fine lettura           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to  stp-cor-doc-bfk-900.
       stp-cor-doc-bfk-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale file [bfk]                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/bfo/fls/ioc/obj/iofbfk"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
